goals.active: Challenge Varg at Drakentelt and retrieve your ancestral horn.
goals.complete: Eir, Garm, and Followed by Night joined me in confronting the Son of Svanir who cheated me out of an heirloom. We defeated Varg and recovered my ancestor's horn. As Romke's descendant, and the horn's rightful owner, I decide what to do with it.
